[-GWWD O.E.S.-]
[-Object Editing System-]

[-I. OBJECT PRICING-]

+1000 for every stat. point raised (ex. the weapon gives +1 strength) 
+100 for every 10pts. of Max Damage. 
+500 for the XDMG ability.
+1000 for the POISON or HEAL abilities.
+2000 for the PARALYSIS and AGING abilities.
+3000 for the LEVEL_DRAIN and CRITICAL abilities.
+1000 for every 25% added to chance of special.
+100 for every 10 uses of an item. (unlimited would be +99,900)
+100 for every added range space.
+100 for every 5pts. of armour added.


[-II. OBJECT WEIGHT-]

-note: A player may hold 10lbs. for every 1pt. of strength, after exceeding   
       this limit they suffer a -1 to hit penalty for every 10lbs. over their
       maximum weight allowance.

Objects are grouped and weighted as follows:

-FEATHER WEIGHT, less than a lb.-
 rings,arrows,potions,etc.

-LIGHT, 1 to 5lbs.-
 wands,daggers,boots,small weapons (ie. daggers),
 light armour (ie. leather), small helmets,
 and small shields.

-MEDIUM, 6 to 15lbs.-
 medium shields,medium armour(ie. chain mail),
 medium helmets,most one-handed weapons (ie staves,swords,bows,etc...).

-HEAVY, 16lbs+.-
 large shields,heavy armour(ie. plate),large helmets,2-handed weapons.

-note: magical armour,etc. should be light no matter the normal weight class.

[-III. OBJECT CLASSES-]

Objects may be put in the classes A-E. A listing of class usage and 
what should appear in each class is presented below.

[-A-]
Classes: ALL
Objects: potions,scrolls,light armour,weapons, and shields.

[-B-]
Classes: Warrior,Hunter,Avatar,Dark Lord
Objects: med-heavy armour,med-heavy shields,med-heavy weapons.

[-C-]
Classes: Enchanter,Seer,Hunter,Dark Lord
Objects: staves,wands,amulets,rings, of a combat nature.

[-D-]
Classes: Acolyte,Avatar,Dark Lord
Objects: staves,wands,amulets,rings, of a protection/healing nature.

[-E-]
Classes: Kensai
Objects: Ancient weapons and armour that only the Kensai may use.

